name: Quantum Spinedream Ascendant
text: The Quantum Spinedream Ascendant emerged, transcending its Psyche-Quantum Spinedancer lineage. Gliding through realms with a prismatic glow, it harmonized the cosmic dissonance, its spires inscribing new dimensions. Whispered legends spoke of an entity, once a weaver of minds, now an architect of realities—a luminescent master of the multiverse.

data.revised_prompt: Envision a complex, multi-dimensional landscape illuminated with numerous vibrant portals, the underlying space-time fabric curling with radiant fractal expansions. At the forefront, a majestic holographic hedgehog shimmers, its entire form boasting prismatic, crystalline glow. An intricate network of advanced celestial patterns trace across the length of its elongated spines. Its eyes, undeniably deeper and enigmatic, cast not mere beams but a whole spectrum of mesmerizing light, symbolic of its evolved mind-controlling abilities.
